{"tid":2008343,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"衞署無參與 不懂清洗","createTime":"2020-05-09T03:38:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-09T05:15:10.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"efafd6fe908e4eb91689eb327354cea0be4dfa11","tid":2008343,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T03:38:46.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200509/AOJQXLDT6C45CKAOIMS72XZFUM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200509%2FAOJQXLDT6C45CKAOIMS72XZFUM%2F&d=i%2FQ10njZfEvfzeNkfPb7d%2FsUKqL2I5G2E%2FT5UXudKlU%3D&h=f22ac161\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200509%2FAOJQXLDT6C45CKAOIMS72XZFUM%2F&h=0863e90b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200509/AOJQXLDT6C45CKAOIMS72XZFUM/</a><br />\n<br />\n衞署無參與 不懂清洗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200509/large/1588955397_884f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200509%2Flarge%2F1588955397_884f.jpg&h=f68fbdc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】立法會衞生事務委會昨日討論武肺防疫措施，醫學界立法會議員陳沛然昨提問，若「銅芯口罩」黏附飛沫或者武肺病毒，應如何消毒口罩，要求當局給予醫學意見。食衞局長陳肇始（圖）回應指，政府派的可重用口罩主要作一般用途，如市民需到醫院或醫療機構，應佩戴即棄外科口罩及N95口罩等。陳沛然反問：「個口罩唔係醫用？咁用嚟做乜？用嚟蒙面呀？」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：創科局辯稱專利改良版<br />\n<br />\n泛民質疑：學蔣麗芸蒸？<br />\n<br />\n陳肇始會上未有正面回答如何清潔口罩，並將問題。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。與重用口罩相關工作，對於口罩詳情「唔係太清楚」。民主。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。望當局交代正常清洗方法，「係咪要響應蔣麗芸議員蒸口。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。減，陳肇始僅稱，重用口罩符合ASTM第一級要求，可清洗60次。<br />\n<br />\n有議員關注日後限聚令等防疫措施一旦撤銷，當局。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。口罩。陳肇始稱，目前市民相當自律，逾九成市民外出時都。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n■記者鄭啟源"},{"pid":"4d8ee9eec0040cf760f31568045b0f228ae43ef7","tid":2008343,"uid":80496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T03:44:38.000Z","msg":"街頭抗爭呢個階段其實已經冇乜用，搞革命應該搞東印度公司，海外建軍。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2007554\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2007554</a><br />\n<br />\n香港人對武力有點誤解 其實譬如阿富汗 美軍是支援出來的<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1962461\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1962461</a><br />\n<br />\n721啟發：我地必須要有獨立武裝單位懲治黑警！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/pgjxGcX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/pgjxGcX</a><br />\n<br />\n發展海外武裝組織<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2007770\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2007770</a>"},{"pid":"941b4f745e58593967238554607a3577fec38a4e","tid":2008343,"uid":88817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:16:28.000Z","msg":"護士仔鬼識咩"},{"pid":"3e274b16cfba2bad653644c3e4b80ce6b9883c06","tid":2008343,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:19:00.000Z","msg":"如市民需到醫院或醫療機構，應佩戴即棄外科口罩及N95口罩等。陳沛然反問：「個口罩唔係醫用？咁用嚟做乜？用嚟蒙面呀？」"},{"pid":"3ba90db54379bc50b73f96d9e24071d704cf5d67","tid":2008343,"uid":36531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:31:27.000Z","msg":"垃圾<br />\n唔通創科局答咩？"},{"pid":"5fc2ea11bd74136588fa9345cad6a3366b8f4b0e","tid":2008343,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:32:01.000Z","msg":"乜都無參與...<br />\n係咪政府無份架?"},{"pid":"7dec16a6a6b736738bb3bf87de14a9fdaa9c027f","tid":2008343,"uid":242050,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T04:32:54.000Z","msg":"原來係支持蒙面法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d468e8d17239ed9d377ccbb2f3c430ea77c09cd6","tid":2008343,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T05:11:06.000Z","msg":"如市民需到醫院或醫療機構，應佩戴即棄外科口罩及N95口罩等。陳沛然反問：「個口罩唔係醫用？咁用嚟做乜？用嚟蒙面呀？」"},{"pid":"e243b9feef0ef437e34c52b8946cf384acd0ad45","tid":2008343,"uid":159876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T05:14:07.000Z","msg":"本身都無咩料到，無咩期望<img src=\"/assets/fac